              ></a>
              <a href="https://pinterest.com" target="_blank"
                ><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i
              ></a>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright-content">
              <p>© Businex 2019. All Right Reserved.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
